<br>
With a last little sniffle, she spoke in the same tone her sister did, &quot;Can you carry me up there, sister?&quot;  Zoe's attention was then turned to Alysia-Samsara as she talked to her.  And a smile was forced to brake through her frown as she nodded with agreement.  With the nod, a few snow flakes which blended in with her wheat-blonde bangs, fell from them. <p><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Zoe</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->, The mystic Lykastian Princess<br>
